description.displayText: Jayla was a great baby sitter for us. Our kids loved her and she was always very responsible. We got alone with her so well that we took her on a couple of vacations to help with the kids. We met her through our daycare center, so we knew she had great experience. She will make a great baby sitter or nanny for anyone.
